@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Intent routing: create event (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Schedule meeting tomorrow at 3pm",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: missing time clarification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Schedule meeting tomorrow",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: query calendar (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What do I have this week?",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: update event (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Move my meeting to Monday at 9am",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: delete event (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Cancel lunch with Sam tomorrow at noon",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: conflict scenario (requires an existing event at the same time)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Schedule demo call today at 3pm",
  "k": 5
}

